name: Jamal REID, Petitioner v. Judge Rose NASTASI-DELFINO [Sic], Respondent

parties: Jamal REID, Petitioner v. Judge Rose NASTASI-DELFINO [Sic], Respondent.

opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 30th day of October, 2013, the Application for Leave to File Original Process is GRANTED, and the Petition for Writ of Mandamus is DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to strike the name of the jurist from the caption.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
